    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "Are you aware that <code>assertTrue(myObject instanceof Object1);</code> and <code>assertEquals(myObject.class, Object1.getClass());</code> are actually different tests? The first accepts myObject being an instance of a subclass of <code>Object1</code>, the later doesn&#39;t."
  }, {
