    "post_id" : 12404650,
    "comment_id" : 16670238,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "as maba points out, consider using Hamcrest. This is more than just so that you have a better working test. Hamcrest also provides much better logging of the failure than standard <code>assertTrue</code>. <code>assertTrue</code> would just say <code>expected true got false</code>, Hamcrest would say <code>expected instanced of XYZ, got instance of ABC</code>"
  } ],
