      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "That&#39;s a trivial assertion and would be a compile error if not true in the example! Usually you want to go down the class hierarchy with <code>instanceof</code>: <code>BaseClass subClass = new SubClass(); assertThat(subClass, isA(SubClass.class));</code>, but it doesn&#39;t compile because <code>SubClass</code> is not <code>? super BaseClass</code>."
